headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Stunt Race Week Unlock: Oppressor Tartan Livery
content:
If rocketing across the sky on a motorcycle with wings wasn't enough to make you stand out, this livery is sure to do the trick. Log in to GTA Online and unlock the gratis Tartan livery for the Pegassi Oppressor.

Check out the Rockstar Newswire for all the details.
